_start":52.69,"time_end":55.81},{"position":24,"content":"Great. And could I ask what your job is?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/24.mp3","time_start":55.81,"time_end":58.84},{"position":25,"content":"Are you a student?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/25.mp3","time_start":58.84,"time_end":59.96},{"position":26,"content":"I've actually just finished my training.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/26.mp3","time_start":59.96,"time_end":62.15},{"position":27,"content":"I'm a hairdresser.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/27.mp3","time_start":62.15,"time_end":63.18},{"position":28,"content":"Oh, right.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/28.mp3","time_start":63.18,"time_end":64.1},{"position":29,"content":"And one more question in this section.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/29.mp3","time_start":64.35,"time_end":66.86},{"position":30,"content":"What is the reason for you coming into town today?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/30.mp3","time_start":66.86,"time_end":69.86},{"position":31,"content":"Actually it's not for shopping today, which would be my normal reason,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/31.mp3","time_start":69.86,"time_end":73.8},{"position":32,"content":"but to see the dentist.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/32.mp3","time_start":74.26,"time_end":75.42},{"position":33,"content":"Right. Thanks.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/33.mp3","time_start":75.42,"time_end":77.43},{"position":34,"content":"Now in this last section I'd like you to give us some ideas about the facilities and arrangements in the city for getting to and from work,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/34.mp3","time_start":78.11,"time_end":87.02},{"position":35,"content":"Any suggestions you have for improvements?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/35.mp3","time_start":87.8,"time_end":90.42},{"position":36,"content":"Well, something I've thought about for some time is that when I do walk and I'm doing a later shift,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/36.mp3","time_start":90.71,"time_end":97.89},{"position":37,"content":"I think the lighting should be better.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/37.mp3","time_start":98.04,"time_end":99.99},{"position":38,"content":"Yes, good point.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/38.mp3","time_start":99.99,"time_end":101.4},{"position":39,"content":"And of course, I think it's a real shame they've been cutting down on the number of footpaths.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/39.mp3","time_start":101.4,"time_end":105.88},{"position":40,"content":"They should have more of those.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/40.mp3","time_start":105.88,"time_end":107.4},{"position":41,"content":"Then people would walk more.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/41.mp3","time_start":107.4,"time_end":108.85},{"position":42,"content":"Yes, right.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/42.mp3","time_start":108.85,"time_end":109.95},{"position":43,"content":"And, I don't think there are enough trains.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/43.mp3","time_start":110.13,"time_end":113.01},{"position":44,"content":"That's why I don't use them - you have to wait so long.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/44.mp3","time_start":113.01,"time_end":115.35},{"position":45,"content":"Thanks.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/45.mp3","time_start":115.54,"time_end":116.5},{"position":46,"content":"And finally I'd like to ask your opinion on cycling.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/46.mp3","time_start":116.72,"time_end":120.2},{"position":47,"content":"As you may know, there's a drive in the city to get more people to cycle to work.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/47.mp3","time_start":120.3,"time_end":124.29},{"position":48,"content":"Right.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/48.mp3","time_start":124.29,"time_end":124.97},{"position":49,"content":"But we realise that there are things which the council, but also employers, might do to help encourage workers to cycle to work.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/49.mp3","time_start":124.97,"time_end":131.92},{"position":50,"content":"Yep.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/50.mp3","time_start":131.92,"time_end":132.62},{"position":51,"content":"Well, I have thought about it and where I work there are no safe places to leave your bikes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/51.mp3","time_start":132.8,"time_end":138.52},{"position":52,"content":"OK.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/52.mp3","time_start":138.52,"time_end":139.48},{"position":53,"content":"And also, I'd have to cycle uphill","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/53.mp3","time_start":139.48,"time_end":142.02},{"position":54,"content":"and on a hot day I'd arrive at work pretty sweaty so I think I'd need a shower somewhere at work.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/54.mp3","time_start":142.02,"time_end":147.36},{"position":55,"content":"Right.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/55.mp3","time_start":147.36,"time_end":148.03},{"position":56,"content":"And I suppose the last thing is that I wouldn't be all that confident about cycling on such busy roads.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/56.mp3","time_start":148.32,"time_end":154.54},{"position":57,"content":"I think I'd like to see you offering training for that, you know.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/57.mp3","time_start":154.77,"time_end":157.91},{"position":58,"content":"I'd feel a lot better about starting if that was the case.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/58.mp3","time_start":157.91,"time_end":161.27},{"position":59,"content":"Well, that's very helpful.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/59.mp3","time_start":161.42,"time_end":163.19},{"position":60,"content":"Thank you very much for your time.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/60.mp3","time_start":163.19,"time_end":164.91},{"position":61,"content":"No problem. Bye.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-10-test-2-part-1-2023-06-13-22-01-33/61.mp3","time_start":164.91,"time_end":166.57}]}